settings.box_content: Officials like you are our #1 priority. For over 25 years, we've built a reputation for delivering quality equipment and apparel for referees and umpires at every level.

You only get one chance to make a first impression, and an official who looks the part gains instant credibility with coaches, players, and fans. When you shop with Gerry Davis Sports, you’ll look and feel like a professional every time you make a call.

We’re serious about this game. We serve amateur sports officials across the world, and make it easier than ever to get the pro look. When you place your order, we move fast, and offer free shipping on orders over $99 in the contiguous United States.

Browse on your computer, tablet, or phone to see up-to-date product availability and pricing. Use advanced filtering and sorting options to find exactly what you need. Convenient and fast checkout makes ordering easy!

Shop by league, group, or conference for professionally logoed uniforms. Customize any shirt with a number or flag. Add hemming service to have pants altered to your specifications. Need custom items ASAP? Rush processing is available.

Returns for store credit and exchanges are FREE within 60 days. Process returns and exchanges quickly and easily online, with return postage provided for your convenience. Returns for refunds within 30 days with a maximum fee of $8.

Super Saver shipping starts as low as $3.50. Orders placed before 12 pm CST (2pm for express shipping) for in-stock products ship the same day. Orders $99+ ship FREE! Need your order ASAP? Express shipping is available!
If you are unhappy with your order for any reason, please let us know. We’ll do our best to go to the replay booth and get the call corrected!

Our growing line of Davis/Gerry Davis Sports branded products are available exclusively at Gerry Davis Sports. When you wear our brands, we cut out the middle man, and you save money on high quality apparel and gear.

Not sure exactly what you need, or what’s best for you? Get expert reviews from professional and amateur officials, access buyer’s guides and Gerry’s recommendations, or contact our knowledgeable customer service team.
We’re here to help! Our dedicated Customer Service can be reached by phone, SMS text, live chat, and e-mail. For the quickest response, contact us between 8:00 am - 5:00 pm CST, Monday - Friday.

After 40 years in MLB, Gerry’s goal is to give back to the game. Gerry Davis Sports is proud to partner with Little League, UMPS CARE, and Wendelstedt Umpire School, and we also give back to YOU on every order with our Score Rewards loyalty program!
Explore our alteration, customization and custom manufacturing capabilities.
Earn points, get rewards - our new loyalty program rewards you for every purchase and other activities!
Fast processing, fair shipping, plus free exchanges & returns*.
